        <mi>a</mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle a}</annotatio=
n>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/ffd2487510aa438433a2579450ab2b3d557e5edc" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:1.23ex; height:1.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle a}">=
</span> is equal to the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Remainder"=
 title=3D"Remainder">remainder</a> of the division of <span class=3D"mwe-ma=
th-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline m=
